{"tid":1736753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好明顯班popo 改變咗策略","createTime":"2019-11-18T19:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T20:50:16.000Z","uid":281968,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59f1e62e48c198436b2bc79259b5db5c8a430e71","tid":1736753,"uid":281968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:39:22.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">消磨我哋嘅意志</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由圍鳩中大開始 佢哋就開始轉策略<br />\n想我哋打從心底放棄、失去希望<br />\n所以就配合埋啲五毛不斷吹奏失敗風氣同製造極端言論分化我哋<br />\n<br />\n其實大家諗清楚<br />\n我哋之前最成功嘅就係<span style=\"color: gold;\">快閃 be water</span><br />\n陣地戰可以話對我哋百害而無一利<br />\n基本上冇一次陣地戰有好結果<br />\n就算中大個晚班狗攻唔入 拉唔到人<br />\n但手足們狂食tg都蝕哂啦 仲有一大堆人受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再盲目留守任何地方<br />\n從來只有快閃係高成效低成本<br />\n例如手足裝修黨鐵站 個站起碼一日半日開唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n塞公路就set啲分段式rb<br />\n等自私自利嘅香港人唔會因架車完全行唔到而落車破壞rb<br />\n吓吓等班狗or藍絲組隊去清<br />\n<br />\n最主要係大家記住班狗一派綠色物體去現場<br />\n實俾佢哋塞住條路1-2個鐘 變相幫手塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 點做都好 最緊要唔好熄咗心入面團怒火<br />\n一直以嚟 港共、建制狗、曱甴、鄉黑做過啲咩<br />\n大家唔好忘記<br />\n仲有犧牲咗嘅義士、被捕被控告嘅手足<br />\n佢哋受苦受難受虐受辱 唔好忘記幫佢哋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">報仇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">心態好重要</span></span><br />\n依排發夢發到攰 咪休息一段時間囉<br />\n對家想打消耗戰、磨時間嘅<br />\n咪睇吓幫個傷啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記抗爭時間愈長 班權貴蝕錢愈多<br />\n只要我哋持續抗爭 唔好放棄 攬炒效果愈強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但戰法就要不斷變 始終班狗唔會坐以待斃<br />\n所以點都要變到唔俾佢哋咬到<br />\n<br />\n由始至終 都係依幾句金科玉律<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不指責<br />\n不被捕</span></span><br />\n過去咗嘅事就當作教訓 唔好再講之前點解做得唔好<br />\n要確保之後改善到、做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560cb66f84430f07e86a6ae52db4347dca04dc91","tid":1736753,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:43:54.000Z","msg":"瞓唔着嘅，不如入嚟睇下<br />\n<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e81914d2da785713ecbbf8c48fd38580c51b394","tid":1736753,"uid":174207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162ad8ac7dff1afdd81fce95450bc583b2cfa1ac","tid":1736753,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a4d700435426cdcbcac3339d47a05722fc21ef","tid":1736753,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"唔係人改變策略，係你自己退化走去守一個根本守唔到嘅地方"},{"pid":"029a81b7692e690a218bcb6edcd97c45e94a1d23","tid":1736753,"uid":33303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a4d700435426cdcbcac3339d47a05722fc21ef","tid":1736753,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"唔係人改變策略，係你自己退化走去守一個根本守唔到嘅地方"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"香港有咩地方係守到?"},{"pid":"d1c0204060726cafef3862ee10a9c592abcdc41d","tid":1736753,"uid":304642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"379f57099c13da0f1972492a641b08bee46fa178","tid":1736753,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:17:27.000Z","msg":"點都唔會覺得輸<br />\n過左廿年仲係咁我再諗諗"},{"pid":"fe7ebfe06cdbac51ae62495a3e38b4bb583b56df","tid":1736753,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029a81b7692e690a218bcb6edcd97c4